ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
Sort(
            Switch(
                galOrderDateFilter.Selected.Value,
                "Last 30 Days",
                Filter(
                    Filter(
                        Filter(
                            'Order Headers',
                            Salesperson.'Primary Email' = User().Email && 'Van No'.Warehouse = varUserVanNo.Van.Warehouse
                        ),
                        'Order Type' = galOrderStatusFilter.Selected.Value
                    ),
                    'Order Date' > DateAdd(
                Today(),
                -30
            )
                ),
                "Last 7 Days",
                Filter(
                    Filter(
                        Filter(
                          'Order Headers',
                           Salesperson.'Primary Email' = User().Email && 'Van No'.Warehouse = varUserVanNo.Van.Warehouse
                        ),
                        'Order Type' = galOrderStatusFilter.Selected.Value
                    ),
                    'Order Date' > DateAdd(
                Today(),
                -7
            )
                ),
                "Today's Orders",
                Filter(
                    Filter(
                        Filter(
                            colOfflineOrderHeader,
                           Salesperson.'Primary Email' = User().Email && 'Van No'.Warehouse = varUserVanNo.Van.Warehouse
                        ),
                        'Order Type' = galOrderStatusFilter.Selected.Value
                    ),
                    'Order Date'>= Today()
                )
            ),
            'Created On',
            SortOrder.Descending
        )
